        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Postgres is the greatest tool of the modern development era.<br>
<!-- -->PGMate has the mission to provide with a <strong>multi-purpose client</strong> that let you:</p>
<ul>
<li>🏋️‍♂️ work with your database</li>
<li>🤖 talk with your data</li>
<li>📋 create SQL workbook that you can share</li>
<li>🧪 bench your queries</li>
<li>✈️ manage migrations</li>
<li>🤓 read articles and learn</li>
</ul>
